# ECC Hardening Fix Pack v3 â€” Noâ€‘Guess Dropâ€‘In

> **Use:** Copy/paste these files into your repo and replace existing ones. Then run the proof steps at the bottom. This kit removes guesswork by enforcing a single, validated data contract from API â†’ UI.

